{
  "stem": "11272.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went over and always asked, do you know anybody from our area, from our village, and the Grosses?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was talking to this guy for 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it turned out it was my brother, Bill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, when he, you know, saw me and recognized me, that night he dug himself under that section, got me, and we got brother Sam.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But by that time, they started evacuating Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was already towards the end of the war, and-- April of 1945.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every time they tried to take us out of the camp-- and we heard shooting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a feeling that anybody they took out, they just shot them in the forest there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we said no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're, we're not going to be moving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First time we got together, we're going to stay together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If they're going to kill us, let them kill us together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, they shot me-- I have a little shrapnel hit in my hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we stayed together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And lo and behold, they start a revolt in the-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother, Bill-- stronger than the, the two of us-- he managed to climb on top of the tower and knock down the, the guard, and managed to help out the partisans.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And by that time, I got very weak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I passed out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I went in a coma.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't even know where I was, what was happening, or nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I woke up maybe a day or two later, when the American tanks arrived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember the noise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember somehow these, these, these tanks pulling up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as I looked up, I saw black faces.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, you know, in Europe, you don't see black faces.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
